\c 32
\s Ithole legolide
\p
\v 1 Abantu sebebonile ukuthi uMozisi uphuzile ukwehla entabeni\x + 24.18. Dute. 9.9.\x*, abantu babuthana kuAroni bathi kuye: Sukuma, usenzele onkulunkulu\x + Seb. 7.40.\x* abazahamba phambi kwethu\x + 13.21.\x*; ngoba uMozisi lo, indoda eyasikhuphula elizweni leGibhithe, kasazi ukuthi yehlelwe yini.
\v 2 UAroni wasesithi kubo: Qamulani amacici egolide\x + Hlu. 8.24-27.\x* asendlebeni zabomkenu, zamadodana enu, lezamadodakazi enu, liwalethe kimi.
\v 3 Bonke abantu basebeqamula amacici egolide ayesendlebeni zabo, bawaletha kuAroni.
\v 4 Wawemukela ezandleni zabo\x + 32.8. Dute. 9.16. Neh. 9.18. Hlab. 106.19. Seb. 7.41. Hlu. 17.3,4. 1 Kho. 12.28.\x*, walibumba ngesikhali sokukhanda, wawenza aba lithole elibunjwe ngokuncibilikisa. Basebesithi: Laba ngonkulunkulu bakho, Israyeli, abakukhuphule elizweni leGibhithe\x + 32.8. Dute. 9.16. Neh. 9.18. Hlab. 106.19. Seb. 7.41. Hlu. 17.3,4. 1 Kho. 12.28.\x*.
\v 5 UAroni eselibonile wakha ilathi phambi kwalo; uAroni wamemezela wathi: Kusasa kuzakuba khona umkhosi weN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Levi 23.2,4,21,37. 2 Kho. 10.20.\x*.
\v 6 Basebevuka ekuseni kakhulu, banikela iminikelo yokutshiswa, basondeza iminikelo yokuthula; abantu bahlala phansi ukudla lokunatha\x + 1 Kor. 10.7.\x*, basebesukuma ukudlala\x + Gen. 26.8. 39.14,17.\x*.
\p
\v 7 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Hamba wehle, ngoba abantu bakho owabakhuphula elizweni leGibhithe\x + Dute. 9.8,12.\x* bonakalisile\x + Gen. 6.11,12. Dute. 4.16. 32.5. Hlu. 2.19. Hos. 9.9.\x*;
\v 8 baphambukile masinyane endleleni engabalaya ngayo\x + 20.3,4,23. Dute. 9.16.\x*; bazenzele ithole elibunjwe ngokuncibilikisa, balikhonza, balihlabela, bathi: Laba ngonkulunkulu bakho, Israyeli, abakukhuphule elizweni leGibhithe\x + 32.4.\x*.
\v 9 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Ngibabonile lababantu, khangela-ke, bangabantu abantamo zilukhuni\x + 33.3,5. 34.9. Dute. 9.6,13. 31.27. 2 Lan. 30.8. Seb. 7.51. Isa. 48.4.\x*.
\v 10 Khathesi-ke ngiyekela\x + Dute. 9.14.\x* ukuze ulaka lwami lubavuthele, ngibaqede\x + 22.24.\x*; kodwa wena ngizakwenza ube yisizwe esikhulu\x + Nani 14.12.\x*.
\v 11 Kodwa uMozisi wancenga ubuso beN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakhe\x + Dute. 9.18,26-29. Hlab. 74.1,2. 106.23.\x* wathi: Kungani, N\nd kosi\nd*, ulaka lwakho lubavuthela abantu bakho owabakhupha elizweni leGibhithe ngamandla amakhulu langesandla esiqinileyo?
\v 12 Kungani amaGibhithe ezakhuluma athi: Wabakhuphela ububi ukubabulala ezintabeni, lokubaqeda ebusweni bomhlaba?\x + Nani 14.13. Dute. 32.27.\x* Phenduka ekuvutheni kolaka lwakho, uzisole ngobubi obumelene labantu bakho\x + 32.14. Gen. 6.6.\x*.
\v 13 Khumbula uAbrahama, uIsaka loIsrayeli, inceku zakho, owazifunga wena kizo wathi kuzo\x + Gen. 22.16. Heb. 6.13.\x*: Ngizakwandisa inzalo yenu njengezinkanyezi zamazulu\x + Gen. 12.7. 13.15. 15.7,18. 26.4. 28.13. 35.11,12. 48.16.\x*, lalelilizwe lonke engikhulume ngalo, ngizalipha inzalo yenu, njalo bazalidla ilifa lalo kuze kube nininini.
\v 14 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasizisola ebubini eyayisithi izabenza ebantwini bayo\x + 32.12. Hlab. 106.45. 1 Lan. 21.15. Jer. 18.8. 26.13,19. Jona 3.10. 4.2.\x*.
\p
\v 15 UMozisi wasetshibilika wehla entabeni\x + Dute. 9.15.\x*, lezibhebhe ezimbili zobufakazi esandleni sakhe; izibhebhe zazibhalwe inhlangothi zazo zombili; zibhalwe ngapha langapha.
\v 16 Lezibhebhe zazingumsebenzi kaNkulunkulu, lombhalo wawungumbhalo kaNkulunkulu, ubazwe ezibhebheni\x + 31.18.\x*.
\v 17 Kwathi uJoshuwa\x + 17.9. 24.13. 33.11.\x* esezwile umsindo wabantu beklabalala, wathi kuMozisi: Kulomsindo wempi enkambeni.
\v 18 Kodwa wathi: Kakusumsindo wokuklabalala kokunqoba, njalo kakusumsindo wokuklabalala kokunqotshwa; ngizwa umsindo wokuhlabelela\x + Jer. 51.14.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Kwasekusithi esesondele enkambeni walibona ithole lokugida\x + Dute. 9.16,17,21.\x*; ulaka lukaMozisi lwaseluvutha, wasezilahla izibhebhe ezandleni zakhe, waziphahlazela phansi kwentaba.
\v 20 Wathatha ithole ababelenzile, walitshisa emlilweni, walichola laze lacoleka, walivuvuzela emanzini, wabanathisa wona abantwana bakoIsrayeli.
\v 21 UMozisi wasesithi kuAroni: Abantu laba benzeni kuwe ukuze ubehlisele isono esikhulu kangaka\x + Gen. 20.9.\x*?
\v 22 UAroni wasesithi: Kalungavuthi ulaka lwenkosi yami; wena uyabazi abantu ukuthi ba\add tshekele\add* ebubini.\x + 14.11. 15.24. 16.2,20. 17.2,4.\x*
\v 23 Ngoba bathi kimi: Senzele onkulunkulu abazahamba phambi kwethu; ngoba uMozisi lo, indoda eyasikhuphula elizweni leGibhithe, kasazi ukuthi yehlelwe yini\x + 32.1.\x*.
\v 24 Ngasengisithi kubo: Loba ngubani olegolide, kabaliqamule\x + 32.2-4.\x*. Basebenginika \add lona\add*. Ngasengiliphosela emlilweni, kwasekuphuma lelithole.
\p
\v 25 Kwathi uMozisi esebonile abantu ukuthi babengabambeki (ngoba uAroni wabayekela bangabambeki ukuze bayangeke kwababengabavukela\x + 2 Lan. 28.19.\x*),
\v 26 uMozisi wasesima esangweni lenkamba, wathi: Loba ngubani ongoweN\nd kosi\nd*, \add keze\add* kimi! Kwasekubuthana kuye wonke amadodana kaLevi.
\v 27 Wasesithi kuwo: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli \add ithi\add*: Ngulowo lalowo kahlome inkemba yakhe ethangazini lakhe, adabule aphenduke esuka esangweni esiya esangweni enkambeni, langulowo lalowo abulale umfowabo, langulowo lalowo umngane wakhe, langulowo lalowo umakhelwane wakhe\x + Nani 25.5. Dute. 33.9.\x*.
\v 28 Amadodana kaLevi asesenza njengelizwi likaMozisi; njalo kwawa ebantwini ngalolosuku abantu abangabazinkulungwane ezintathu.
\v 29 UMozisi wasesithi: Lizehlukanisele iN\nd kosi\nd* lamuhla, ngoba ngulowo lalowo ubemelene lendodana yakhe amelane lomfowabo, ukuze aphe isibusiso phezu kwenu lamuhla\x + Nani 25.11,12,13. Dute. 13.6-11. Zek. 13.3. Mat. 10.37.\x*.
\p
\v 30 Kwasekusithi kusisa uMozisi wathi ebantwini: Lina lenze isono esikhulu\x + 32.21,32. 1 Sam. 12.20.\x*; khathesi sengizakwenyukela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni; mhlawumbe\x + 2 Sam. 16.12. Amos 5.15.\x* ngingenza inhlawulo yokuthula ngesono senu\x + Nani 25.13.\x*.
\v 31 UMozisi wasebuyela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Dute. 9.18.\x* wathi: Maye! Lababantu bonile isono esikhulu, bazenzele onkulunkulu begolide\x + 20.23.\x*.
\v 32 Khathesi-ke, uba uthethelela isono sabo - kodwa uba kungenjalo\x + Gen. 30.27.\x*, ake ungesule\x + Roma 9.3.\x* egwalweni lwakho olubhalileyo\x + Hlab. 56.8. 69.28. 139.16. Dan. 12.1. Fil. 4.3. Isam. 3.5. 13.8. 17.8. 20.12,15. 21.27.22.19.\x*.
\v 33 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Owonileyo kimi ngizamesula egwalweni lwami\x + Hez. 18.4,20.\x*.
\v 34 Kodwa hamba-ke, ukhokhele abantu baye lapho engikhulume lawe ngakho; khangela, ingilosi yami izahamba phambi kwakho\x + 33.2,3. 14.19.\x*. Kanti mhla ngiphindisela ngizaphindisela isono sabo phezu kwabo.
\v 35 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasibatshaya abantu ngoba babenze ithole, uAroni ayelenzile.